&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot;&gt;Our Customer Success team is dedicated to empowering our clients to achieve their unique learning goals. We partner with organisations globally to ensure they unlock maximum value from our platform, driving long-term adoption, retention, and growth. Acting as trusted advisors, the team focuses on strategic enablement and fostering an open, collaborative environment to support our customers at every stage of their learning journey.&lt;/p&gt;
