&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;12,0,0&quot;&gt;Portfolio Management: Own a portfolio of Enterprise customers, ensuring they achieve defined business outcomes and realize measurable value through LearnUpon.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
