&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;12,3,0&quot;&gt;Consultative Guidance: Act as a trusted advisor, using curiosity and insight to guide customers toward improved outcomes and navigate change.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using AI tools to streamline tasks and improve efficiencies&lt;/li&gt;
