&lt;p&gt;Reporting directly to the VP of Revenue, you will be the single-threaded owner of the entire funnel for partner-generated and partner-influenced revenue. In this role, you will transition the partnership function into a highly accountable pipeline engine, driving strategic alignment with GTM leadership and breaking down silos across reporting, processes, and funnel management. Your leadership will be a direct catalyst for our growth goals, transforming indirect channels into a reliable, high-performing contributor to our global revenue targets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
