&lt;li&gt;Strategic Proximity: Ability to work from our Dublin, Ireland office to provide hands-on guidance to the local team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accountability: Comfortable being held to the same rigorous forecasting and pipeline standards as direct sales leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
