&lt;li&gt;Influencer &amp;amp; Community Management: Own CreateUpon audience research, partnering with L&amp;amp;D influencers and managing community presence on LinkedIn and Reddit. Social listening and engagement for CreateUpon.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Growth Experimentation: Rapidly deploy, measure, and iterate on growth experiments across the organic funnel, using data to double down on what works.&lt;/li&gt;
