&lt;li&gt;Lifecycle Growth Engine (Learn-Try-Buy-Renew): Build and automate cross-lifecycle nurture tracks. Beyond initial onboarding, focus on driving long-term retention and expansion by mapping content and triggers to each stage of the Learn-Try-Buy-Renew journey, ensuring u

