&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;9&quot;&gt;Our Finance team is vital to our Company and is responsible for keeping the financial operations of the business running smoothly. We are currently in an exciting phase of transformation, embracing AI-driven workflows and automation. This is a unique opportunity for a self-motivated individual to join a forward-thinking team that is already leveraging cutting-edge technology to shape the future of SaaS finance.&lt;/p&gt;
