&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;13,2,0&quot;&gt;Process Optimisation: Play a pivotal role in transitioning to our new billing process, ensuring high accuracy in legacy systems during the final 3-month countdown while leading UAT, data validation, and auditing billing workflows for automation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;13,3,0&quot;&gt;Operational Collaboration: Partner with cross-functional teams like Sales, Customer Experience, and Legal to quickly resolve complex billing issues&lt;/p&gt;
